Announcements, publications and subscriptions can be defined using XML files. 
This folder contains one example file with publication definition and another with subscription definition.

Publication
-type: booleanHashtable
-validity: long[period in ms] || -1[infinity]
-attribute name: string
-attribute operator: "EQUAL"
-attribute type: string || integer || long || double || float || boolean

Subscription
-type: booleanTriplet
-validity: long[period in ms] || -1[infinity]
-attribute name: string
-attribute operator: "EQUAL" || "GREATER_THAN" || "GREATER_OR_EQUAL" || "LESS_THAN" || "LESS_OR_EQUAL" || "BETWEEN" || CONTAINS_STRING" || "ENDS_WITH_STRING" || "STARTS_WITH_STRING"
-attribute type: string || integer || long || double || float || boolean

Announcement
-type: booleanTriplet
-validity: long[period in ms] || -1[infinity]
-attribute name: string
-attribute operator: "EQUAL" || "GREATER_THAN" || "GREATER_OR_EQUAL" || "LESS_THAN" || "LESS_OR_EQUAL" || "BETWEEN" || CONTAINS_STRING" || "ENDS_WITH_STRING" || "STARTS_WITH_STRING"
-attribute type: string || integer || long || double || float || boolean